overview: In a post human world, digital remnants of a long ago past run through the artificial mind of the global digital consciousness like a dream.  Created to be like their creator, this consciousness now tumbles through nightmares, illusions, home movies, memories, daydreams and amalgamations of a self image.
tagline: "WHO OWNS THE GRAVEYARD?" is the final album by elvis depressedly.
title: Who Owns The Graveyard
